# PR80 Application - Project Overview

This is a monorepo for the PR80 application, structured using pnpm workspaces. The project consists of the following main parts:

## Applications
- **Web App**: Located in [apps/web](mdc:apps/web) - The frontend web application
- **API**: Located in [apps/api](mdc:apps/api) - The backend API service

## Packages
- **UI Library**: Located in [packages/ui](mdc:packages/ui) - Shared UI components and design system

## Key Files
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Root package with workspace scripts
- [pnpm-workspace.yaml](mdc:pnpm-workspace.yaml) - Workspace configuration
